channel.title: ::players reveals alL!
channel.description: Well, i typed in ::players on my server, and it came up with a list. there were 22 people online, only 2 acuall people, the rest were null What is null? i belive i heard there websites. how can i get rid of them? they lag my server to death.

item.title: ::players reveals alL!
item.dc:creator: @Path_To_Pain Path To Pain
item.description:
@Path_To_Pain wrote:

or alternatively in noob language a null is usually a something or someone connecting your server. If the connection is lost suddenly then the null will be put in place for the person/connecting peer. There is a tutorial on how to remove the nulls. I will have a look for you
